text: David W. Panuelo (born 1964) is a Micronesian politician. He was the ninth President of the Federated States of Micronesia. His term started on 11 May 2019 and ended on 11 May 2023. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1964 births Category:Presidents of the Federated States of Micronesia Category:Current national leaders
